name: 20 to Catadise (Cat Paradise)
description:
Click, and drag to launch Cali Cat! Get as high as possible in 20 seconds! The Checker Areas are where you touch or click, with several as you go higher and higher.

Hello! This is SkaldingDelight with my second ever Game Jam submission, come check it out and my other game, 201!

https://imacer.itch.io/201

Catadise was submitted for the 20 Second Game Jam, in November 2022, and focuses on the bonus Theme of 'Boingy, boingy"

https://itch.io/jam/20-second-game-jam

https://ko-fi.com/skald Support Games like this!

Assets used are public domain and listed below, Check it out!
